                            <comment id="12719460" author="noble.paul" created="Mon, 15 Jun 2009 09:41:41 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;update.processor is not for RequestHandler it is common across all requesthandlers&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12735738" author="gsingers" created="Mon, 27 Jul 2009 20:44:53 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Seems like this is fixed in example right?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &amp;lt;!-- An example dedup update processor that creates the &quot;id&quot; field on the fly&lt;br/&gt;
       based on the hash code of some other fields.  This example has overwriteDupes&lt;br/&gt;
       set to false since we are using the id field as the signatureField and Solr&lt;br/&gt;
       will maintain uniqueness based on that anyway. --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;!--&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;updateRequestProcessorChain name=&quot;dedupe&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;processor class=&quot;org.apache.solr.update.processor.SignatureUpdateProcessorFactory&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;bool name=&quot;enabled&quot;&amp;gt;true&amp;lt;/bool&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;str name=&quot;signatureField&quot;&amp;gt;id&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;bool name=&quot;overwriteDupes&quot;&amp;gt;false&amp;lt;/bool&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;str name=&quot;fields&quot;&amp;gt;name,features,cat&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;str name=&quot;signatureClass&quot;&amp;gt;org.apache.solr.update.processor.Lookup3Signature&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/processor&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;processor class=&quot;solr.LogUpdateProcessorFactory&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;processor class=&quot;solr.RunUpdateProcessorFactory&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/updateRequestProcessorChain&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  --&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please close if this is the case.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12739284" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Wed, 5 Aug 2009 01:50:50 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think this has been addressed?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;update.processor is not for RequestHandler it is common across all requesthandlers&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No - I&apos;m talking about the processor chain that you configure on the handler with the update.processor param.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12739288" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Wed, 5 Aug 2009 01:55:37 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Hmm - I swear I had responded to you when you originally asked that Grant - but not seeing my reply here or on the dev list ...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thats not the example I&apos;m talking about - I&apos;m talking about linking an update req handler to the dedupe chain. If you just uncomment that example, you won&apos;t get far because it won&apos;t be used by anything - they will use the default chain assigned to null.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12746547" author="lancenorskog" created="Sun, 23 Aug 2009 04:02:00 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I am all for examples, but the example schema.xml and solrconfig.xml cannot contain examples for every possible use of the tools. Maybe this could go in the wiki instead?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12746561" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Sun, 23 Aug 2009 06:03:59 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not looking for every possible example.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But since we give an example of a custom update chain, it seems we might give an example or pointer on how to actually put it in use? Its kind of a frustrating example otherwise.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be in the Wiki as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12749189" author="billa" created="Sat, 29 Aug 2009 22:41:39 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I had actually come across an example in the Wiki when I was looking for information on update processor:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://wiki.apache.org/solr/Deduplication?highlight=%28updateprocessor%29#head-177c1b1e490e1192f41d9ab0e037b05e1567a35d&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://wiki.apache.org/solr/Deduplication?highlight=%28updateprocessor%29#head-177c1b1e490e1192f41d9ab0e037b05e1567a35d&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12753786" author="gsingers" created="Thu, 10 Sep 2009 20:45:20 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Mark,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch seems fine to me.  Can we finish this one off?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12754150" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Fri, 11 Sep 2009 15:30:39 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;thanks for the review - committed r813854&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
